# Secrets — D9: connection strings live out-of-band, never committed.
# `.env` holds the values the config's env:<VAR> references resolve to;
# `.env.example` is the committed template. `secrets/` + *.conn back file:<path> refs.
.env
secrets/
*.conn
!.env.example
